    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Let us wor-ship the Word, O__ ye faith--ful, prais--ing___ Him that with the Fa-ther and Spir-it is co--be-gin---ning--less___ God, Who was born of a pure Vir-gin that we all__ be__ saved; for__ He was pleased to__ mount__ the Cross in the flesh that__ He__ as--sumed,__ ac-cept----ing___ thus to__ en-dure____ death. And by His glo-ri-ous ris---ing, He al-so willed__ to__ res--ur--rect____ the_____ dead."
